**Ivan's cases:**
- Case: {what happened, outcome}
  Source: {full path to file in repository}
  Key detail: {most specific/memorable element}

**External cases:**
- Case: {company/person — what happened — outcome}
  URL: {real link}
  Year: {year}
  Why it fits: {one sentence connection to thesis}

## SAVE (REQUIRED)

